comment.author: 33044226@N08
comment._content: Vesta Tilley was an actor and married Walter de Frece in London in 1890 - so this would probably be a publicity photograph rather than a honeymoon photo. Her husband was also active in public life. See the wikipedia article for more! en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vesta_Tilley
